description: What a privilege to learn from the Master, Bob Wilber, to hear his stories of first-hand jazz experiences and life experiences . . . a wonderful opportunity made possible by Bob and his wife, the singer Joanne "Pug" Horton, when the Wilbers visited New York City in autumn 2015.  Recorded by Michael Steinman for JAZZ LIVES (http://jazzlives.wordpress.com).
title: BOB WILBER REMEMBERS, PART TWO (September 27, 2015)
